{"tid":2370681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中方強烈譴責】中方對涉港問題表現惡劣美方人員及直系親屬實施制裁","createTime":"2021-01-18T08:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T09:38:20.000Z","uid":24660,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"66f2b1496f6fc34f8ba214e5af0a6a588444db62","tid":2370681,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:11:19.000Z","msg":"美國日前宣布，制裁6名中國與香港特區政府人員後，中國決定對在涉港問題上表現惡劣、負有主要責任的美國行政部門官員、國會人員、非政府組織人員及其直系親屬，實施對等制裁。<br />\n<br />\n外交部發言人華春瑩表示，美方有關行徑公然插手香港事務，粗暴干涉中國內政和中國司法主權，嚴重違反國際法和國際關係基本準則，中方堅決反對，強烈譴責，強調香港是法治社會，法律面前人人平等，有法必依、違法必究是法治的基本要求，堅定支持香港特區有關部門依法打擊違法犯罪活動，維護法律權威，捍衛國家安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571022-20210118.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571022-20210118.htm&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=411fe487\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571022-20210118.htm&h=715cc84c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571022-20210118.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1aba898f87bb11fe0b255c15a18c1bea5b96b880","tid":2370681,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:13:37.000Z","msg":"有無名單？"},{"pid":"4e431561fe9d60d76d24450f5fe71e3125539f1f","tid":2370681,"uid":27432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:14:11.000Z","msg":"20號之後, 美國正式納入中國國土, 到時呢班美官就會趕出中國領土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c95c70ce7911e22b814e445dd640b479788afd","tid":2370681,"uid":35087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:14:43.000Z","msg":"who<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 